gov.nih.nlm.meme.client
Interface ClientConstants

All Superinterfaces:
MEMEConstants
public interface ClientConstants
extends MEMEConstants

This interface holds constants commonly used by MEME client. Many of the constants define property names that appear in the property file.

Author:
MEME Group

PROTOCOL_HANDLER

public static final String PROTOCOL_HANDLER
Name of the property which indicates the protocol handler class used by clients. The value of the property with this name should be a fully qualified name for a class implementing MEMERequestClient.
